{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a huge machine city, where countless small robots work hard to maintain the operation of the machine tower. After operating for countless years , the machine tower has become older and more dangerous day by day. Our main character, an unknown screwing robot (which can be understood as a screw worker) from the bottom of the machine tower, is about to embark on an adventure in the tower.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Challenge rich mechanical guards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Various mechanical guards have unique deformation and attack methods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452900/extras/JiXieShouWeiE.gif?t=1737509282\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Rich prop combinations and cultivation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are multiple weapons and different skills available</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452900/extras/JiNengE.gif?t=1737509282\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unstoppable mechanical traps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The machine tower is becoming increasingly old. In the dilapidated tower, there are various mechanisms and traps hidden. Pay close attention to safety and be careful when sailing for ten thousand years!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452900/extras/XianJinE.gif?t=1737509282\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fight against unique bosses</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each boss is an experienced management expert with their own unique skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3452900/extras/BOSSE.gif?t=1737509282\" /></p><